1965;;Strange Bedfellows;;American;;Melvin Frank;;Rock Hudson, Gina Lollobrigida, Gig Young;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strange_Bedfellows_(1965_film);;A wealthy American (Hudson) and a bohemian Italian woman (Lollobrigida) meet in London, and impulsively marry. Then finding they have virtually nothing in common they separate. Seven years later, just days before the divorce is due to be finalized, they meet again and begin to rekindle the romance.